column16: Nomar Mazara doubles (13) on a line drive to center fielder Kevin Kiermaier, deflected by left fielder Corey Dickerson.
Elvis Andrus grounds out, shortstop Tim Beckham to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Shin-Soo Choo homers (6) on a fly ball to right center field.
Jared Hoying grounds out softly, first baseman Logan Morrison to pitcher Jose De Leon.
Jonathan Lucroy flies out to right fielder Steven Souza Jr.
Rougned Odor grounds out to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Adrian Beltre lines out to left fielder Corey Dickerson.
Elvis Andrus grounds into a force out, first baseman Logan Morrison to shortstop Tim Beckham.   Shin-Soo Choo out at 2nd.    Elvis Andrus to 1st.
Shin-Soo Choo singles on a ground ball to center fielder Kevin Kiermaier.   Robinson Chirinos scores.    Jared Hoying scores.
Jared Hoying walks.  Wild pitch by pitcher Jose De Leon.   Robinson Chirinos to 3rd.
Robinson Chirinos singles on a ground ball to left fielder Corey Dickerson.
